### Arabic

ذَٰلِكَ بِأَنَّهُمْ كَرِهُوا۟ مَآ أَنزَلَ ٱللَّهُ فَأَحْبَطَ أَعْمَـٰلَهُمْ

### English

That is because they detest what Allah has revealed, so He has rendered their deeds void.